LIST. WHEN SIMPLE RATIOS ARE TRANSLATED THE DENOMINATOR WILL BE DEFINED        1
BY OUTPUTTING MT IN FIELD 5 AND ZA IN FIELD 6. THE FOLLOWING LIST SHOULD       1
ONLY BE USED TO DEFINE COMPLEX RATIOS.                                         1
